==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: jingoism
<hw>jin"go*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
policy of the Jingoes, so called. See <er>Jingo</er>, 2.</def>
<mark>[Cant, Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>A bellicose patriotism;
aggressive chauvinism; belligerence in international
relations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>jingoist</ent>⟦br⟧
